{"id":6760,"date":"2025-04-12T15:47:40","date_gmt":"2025-04-12T08:47:40","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/supership.vn\/?p=6760"},"modified":"2025-05-22T09:28:59","modified_gmt":"2025-05-22T02:28:59","slug":"tong-hop-cach-lam-affiliate-amazon-hieu-qua-cho-nguoi-moi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/supership.vn\/tin-tuc\/tong-hop-cach-lam-affiliate-amazon-hieu-qua-cho-nguoi-moi.html","title":{"rendered":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m Affiliate Amazon hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Affiliate Amazon (hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Amazon Associates) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ec1n online b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng v\u00e0 uy t\u00edn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd hoa h\u1ed3ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, Affiliate Amazon\u00a0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, <a href=\"http:\/\/supership.vn\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><em><span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>SuperShip<\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/span><\/a> s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m Affiliate Amazon t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t, t\u1eeb A \u0111\u1ebfn Z, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u, chi ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ngay.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><\/h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b>1. Affiliate Amazon\u00a0 l\u00e0 g\u00ec? V\u00ec sao ai c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n tham gia?<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Affiliate Amazon\u00a0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb li\u00ean k\u1ebft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Amazon, cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn hoa h\u1ed3ng khi c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua h\u00e0ng qua link gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. M\u1ed7i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 hoa h\u1ed3ng kh\u00e1c nhau, dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 1% \u0111\u1ebfn 10%.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>Nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Affiliate Amazon thu h\u00fat:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a Amazon<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: V\u1edbi uy t\u00edn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng trung th\u00e0nh l\u1edbn, Amazon gi\u00fap c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Affiliate d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua v\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m cho vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n, v\u00ec kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u00edt ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i khi mua s\u1eafm.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m phong ph\u00fa<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Amazon cung c\u1ea5p v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed3 gia d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, s\u00e1ch, v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m s\u1ed1, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Affiliate l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng m\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i cao<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Amazon c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ed1t nh\u1edd v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 tin c\u1eady v\u00e0 uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Affiliate d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hoa h\u1ed3ng nh\u1edd v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng mua h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Thanh to\u00e1n \u0111\u00fang h\u1ea1n, minh b\u1ea1ch, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Amazon \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o thanh to\u00e1n hoa h\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00fang h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 minh b\u1ea1ch, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c tr\u00ean to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u, gi\u00fap m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia ki\u1ebfm thu nh\u1eadp d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>Thu nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb Affiliate Amazon ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Ng\u00e1ch b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn &amp; L\u01b0u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng truy c\u1eadp<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Ch\u1ecdn ng\u00e1ch ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 \u00edt c\u1ea1nh tranh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng thu h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u01b0u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng truy c\u1eadp cao t\u1eeb website ho\u1eb7c blog c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ki\u1ebfm hoa h\u1ed3ng s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed9i dung &amp; SEO<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: T\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i dung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u SEO gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n thu h\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u0103ng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm hoa h\u1ed3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i cao gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u hoa h\u1ed3ng khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng nh\u1ea5p v\u00e0o li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n mua h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/tin-tuc\/top-10-trang-tiep-thi-lien-ket-tai-viet-nam-va-nuoc-ngoai.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #0000ff;\"><em><strong>Xem th\u00eam: Top 10 trang ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Amazon-Associates.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6680 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Amazon-Associates.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Amazon - Top 10 trang ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb li\u00ean k\u1ebft\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Amazon-Associates.png 800w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Amazon-Associates-300x188.png 300w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Amazon-Associates-768x480.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b>2. C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m Affiliate Amazon cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi trang web ho\u1eb7c k\u00eanh n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft g\u1ed1c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Amazon Associates \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Amazon.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: \u0110\u0103ng K\u00fd Tham Gia Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng Tr\u00ecnh Amazon Associates<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, b\u1ea1n truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o trang web<\/span><em><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/affiliate-program.amazon.com\/\"> Amazon Associates<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o n\u00fat \u201cSign up\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Amazon, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n m\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tham gia ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Chuan-anh-trong-noi-dung-Website-8.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6764 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Chuan-anh-trong-noi-dung-Website-8.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m Affiliate Amazon hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Chuan-anh-trong-noi-dung-Website-8.png 800w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Chuan-anh-trong-noi-dung-Website-8-300x188.png 300w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Chuan-anh-trong-noi-dung-Website-8-768x480.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: Cung C\u1ea5p Th\u00f4ng Tin T\u00e0i Kho\u1ea3n<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111i\u1ec1n c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 Amazon c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thanh to\u00e1n \u0111\u00fang cho b\u1ea1n. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Amazon c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 thanh to\u00e1n, h\u00e3y nh\u1ea5p v\u00e0o \u201cSelect Different Address\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu th\u00f4ng tin ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n, ch\u1ecdn &#8220;The payee listed above&#8221;. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i, ch\u1ecdn &#8220;Someone else \u2013 I need to enter their information&#8221; v\u00e0 nh\u1eadp th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean l\u1ea1c m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Chuan-anh-trong-noi-dung-Website-13.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6769\" src=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Chuan-anh-trong-noi-dung-Website-13.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m Affiliate Amazon\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Chuan-anh-trong-noi-dung-Website-13.png 800w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Chuan-anh-trong-noi-dung-Website-13-300x188.png 300w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Chuan-anh-trong-noi-dung-Website-13-768x480.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Cung C\u1ea5p Th\u00f4ng Tin V\u1ec1 Trang Web v\u00e0 \u1ee8ng D\u1ee5ng<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00eam t\u1ed1i \u0111a 50 trang web ho\u1eb7c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng di \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong m\u1ee5c n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1n c\u1ea3 link \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c trang m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i n\u01a1i b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Amazon.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x